8699 - Membership Organisations, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > THERAPY FOCUS LTD. is an Australian public company. Its operations cover membership organisations, not elsewhere classified. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. THERAPY FOCUS LTD. is headquartered in Bentley, Western Australia. It is headed by CEO Fiona Julie Payne. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $31.29 million. Its net loss totalled $2.05 million. THERAPY FOCUS LTD. forms part of the services industry sector.
